  <!-- What We Do -->
  <section id="what-we-do">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <p class="section-label">What We Do</p>
      <div class="section-title">TECHNICAL GUIDANCE.<br><em>REAL OUTCOMES.</em></div>
      <p style="max-width:640px;color:var(--off-w);font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:0;">
        Arbiter IO provides strategic technical guidance across the full computing spectrum. We don't just advise — we've built and run these systems ourselves, at scale, for the organizations that can't afford to get it wrong.
      </p>
      <div class="services-grid">
        <div class="service-card fade-up">
          <div class="service-num">01</div>
          <h3 class="service-title">Infrastructure Strategy</h3>
          <p class="service-body">Architecture design and strategic planning for computing infrastructure at any scale — from a single application running at the edge to massively scalable service provider grade systems. We've built both ends of that spectrum and everything in between.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card fade-up">
          <div class="service-num">02</div>
          <h3 class="service-title">AI & Cloud Infrastructure</h3>
          <p class="service-body">Kubernetes, hybrid cloud, bare metal AI deployment, and ransomware resilience. Deep hands-on expertise from mainframe-era fundamentals through modern AI cluster design. We understand what runs underneath the abstraction layers.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card fade-up">
          <div class="service-num">03</div>
          <h3 class="service-title">Business & Product Turnarounds</h3>
          <p class="service-body">We've built successful startups, led business turnarounds, and driven product pivots. Our team has held CTO, VP of Sales, SVP, and operational leadership roles — we bring the full picture, not just the technical view.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card fade-up">
          <div class="service-num">04</div>
          <h3 class="service-title">Go-To-Market & Revenue Strategy</h3>
          <p class="service-body">Channel development, distributor programs, enterprise sales strategy, and Federal market engagement. Decades of enterprise sales leadership at EMC, NetApp, Tintri, and Diamanti inform every engagement.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card fade-up">
          <div class="service-num">05</div>
          <h3 class="service-title">Deployment & Operations</h3>
          <p class="service-body">From PoC to production. Multi-tenant cloud platforms, edge deployments, HA clustering, Cisco UCS, NetApp, EMC, and beyond. We've managed infrastructure for hundreds of enterprise clients nationally and internationally.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card fade-up">
          <div class="service-num">06</div>
          <h3 class="service-title">Technical Due Diligence</h3>
          <p class="service-body">M&A technical assessments, acquisition integration planning, migration strategy, and platform rationalization. We've led due diligence at the CTO level for acquisition targets and have the scars to prove it.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
