        <!-- Phil -->
        <div class="founder-card fade-up">
          <div class="founder-name">PHIL TRICKOVIC</div>
          <div class="founder-title">Co-Founder &nbsp;·&nbsp; Revenue & Go-To-Market</div>
          <p class="founder-bio">
            Phil is an enterprise technology sales and revenue executive with a 30-year track record of building teams, cracking new markets, and driving growth at companies that defined the storage and infrastructure industry. He began his career in technology operations — as a DBA at EDS and IT Director at the height of the dot-com era — before making the transition into enterprise sales where he found his calling.
          </p>
          <p class="founder-bio">
            At EMC he spent nearly a decade building sales teams across the Southeast. At NetApp he covered named and commercial enterprise accounts. At Tintri he rose from Regional Sales Manager to Vice President of Worldwide Sales and Marketing, building the global revenue organization and go-to-market strategy that took the company through its most aggressive growth period. He then served as VP of Sales at Diamanti during the Kubernetes infrastructure wave before returning to Tintri as SVP of Revenue.
          </p>
          <p class="founder-bio">
            Phil's domain is the full revenue cycle — channel strategy, distributor relationships, Federal market development, Latin American expansion, enterprise account management, and the kind of direct enterprise selling that only comes from 30 years in the room with CIOs and CTOs.
          </p>
